Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That wasn't the reaction \NI was expecting.}Phản ứng có hơi khác dự tính...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.57,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Meowtaro is the heir to a major corporation.}Nyantaro là thừa kế tập đoàn lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.37,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{He eats fish every day, so he's tired of it!}Nên ngày nào cũng ăn cá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.80,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{I don't think that's part of the backstory...}Mới nghe về gia thế đó luôn.
