Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.82,Game_Text/Dialogue,Meowtaro,0,0,0,,{I've never had anything like it...}Lần đầu tiên mới nếm vị này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:15.31,Game_Text/Dialogue,Meowtaro,0,0,0,,{You must know about a world \NI'm unfamiliar with.}Hẳn em là người hiểu biết thế giới lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.30,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{What does that even mean?}Vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.13,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{What are you all doing?}Mọi người làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Kurusu-san.}Kurusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.37,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Office hours are over.}Giờ làm xong rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.82,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Why are you all here?}Sao còn ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:30.57,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{I was having them try out \Nthe Meowtaro game I made.}Tôi đang nhờ họ chơi thử con game Nyantaro mới làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Want to try it, Kurusu-san?}Em thử không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.33,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{A Meowtaro game?!}Nyantaro game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:39.33,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I do! I want to play! Please let me play it!}Em muốn! Hãy cho em chơi thử!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.33,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(88,230)\fs12\c&HC188E6&\3c&HF4F7F4&\shad0\an1}{Meowtaro:}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.33,Game_Text/Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{I could steal these lips\Nin a heartbeat.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Nếu là vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.34,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Who?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.29,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{This is anthropomorphic hottie Meowtaro!}Nyantaro nhân hoá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:50.09,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{It'll let us develop \Nthe latent otome game market!}Nó giúp ta phát triển mảng otome game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.05,Italics,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Meowtaro...? Hot...? Anthropomorphic...?}Nyantaro? Nóng bỏng? Nhân hoá?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.85,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{My Meowtaro... what in the world...?}Nyantaro... chuyện gì vậy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.21,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{This isn't development. It's pandering.}Đây không phải là phát triển mà là phát lùi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.85,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It doesn't convey a fraction of \NMeowtaro's actual appeal.}Nó không thể hiện được chút sự dễ thương nào cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:07.11,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It's more likely to chase off \Nexisting fans than develop new ones.}Nó sẽ đuổi fan thay vì hút fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.99,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It's idiocy.}Ngu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.22,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Do you really think we can \Nopen up new opportunities}Nếu chúng ta có thể mở ra cơ hội
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.86,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{by being so beholden to old fans \Nthat we never try anything new?}bằng cách tri ân fan gạo cội\N bằng một làn gió mới thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.70,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It's a question of methodology.}Vấn đề là ở cách làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.10,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{This would honestly be better off \Nas a completely distinct project...}Cái thứ này nên tách biệt thành một dự án khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.62,Main - Top,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Let's keep on playing, Zakishino!}Tiếp tục thôi Zakishiro.
