Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:25.88,Game_Text/Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{The culture festival is ending...\NThere's something I need to tell to you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.05,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Are we gonna get a confession \Nafter the festival?!}Định tỏ tình sau lễ hội văn hoá hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure. It feels a little too soon \Nfor things to be ending...}Không biết nữa. Vẫn còn nhiều mới đến ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.14,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{But it's a private meeting on the rooftop!}Nhưng mà gặp gỡ bí mật 2 người trên sân thượng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.14,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{On the rooftop...}Trên sân thượng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Meeting in private...}Gặp gỡ bí mật...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.30,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That sounds familiar.}Nghe quen quen...
