Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.77,Game_Text/Dialogue,Meowtaro,0,0,0,,{Let's always be good senpai and kohai, okay?}Hãy là tiền bối và hậu bối tốt của nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This line...}Đoạn này...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That line...}Đoạn này...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.78,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's always be good coworkers, okay?}Hãy là tiền bối và hậu bối tốt của nhau nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.78,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's kinda similar!}Nghe quen quen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.93,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Aw, man, we got rejected before the confession.}Bị từ chối trước khi tỏ tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Rejected...}Từ chối...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Before confessing...}Trước khi tỏ tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Rejected?}Từ chối?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Before confessing...?}Trước khi tỏ tình?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I rejected him?! \NThat's not what I was trying to do...!}Mình đã từ chối em ấy?\N Ý mình khi đó không phải thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that what Shinozaki-san felt at the time?!}Không lẽ lúc đó Shinozaki định làm thế thật?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.92,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I really was rejected?! \NThat's what really happened?!}Mình bị từ chối sau? Biết ngay mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:27.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And after I had tried to forget all about it!}Và sau đó mình còn cố quên đi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.32,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{What's with you two?}Hai người bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:35.20,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Hold it right there. It's too soon to give up.}Nào nào, vẫn còn sớm để từ bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.20,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{I know you two must have realized it.}Có vẻ hai người đã nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.20,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{There's still a while before the ending, \Nand you haven't confessed yet...}Vẫn còn nhiều trước khi đến \Nending và vẫn chưa tỏ tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:46.49,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{So you can still seal the deal yet! \NYour chance is still out there...}Thế nên chưa có gì quyết định cả,\N bây giờ mới là lúc nắm lấy cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.71,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Or do you mean to tell me...}Hay là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:51.84,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{that you two don't love Meowtaro that much?!}hai người không yêu Nyantaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.97,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{I mean, we don't.}Thì đúng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hadn't confessed yet...}Vẫn chưa tỏ tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's still a chance...}Vẫn còn cơ hội...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I hadn't confessed yet!}Mình vẫn chưa tỏ tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.61,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's still a chance!}Vẫn còn cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's right! We haven't been rejected yet!}Phải nhỉ! Vẫn chưa bị từ chối mà
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I agree!}Đúng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:12.22,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Is there a reason you guys are so into this?}Hai người có vẻ hơi hào hứng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.11,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It's not even the real Meowtaro.}Đó không phải Nyantaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That video game was fun.}Trò này thú vị ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It sure was.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.68,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I liked how they ended up \Ntogether in the end.}Cuối cùng cũng đến được với nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.94,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:33.38,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What was it that you wanted to tell me before?}Chuyện lúc trước em muốn nói là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:49.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I was wondering if we'd always \Njust be a senpai and a kohai.}Em tự hỏi quan hệ giữa hai ta sẽ mãi như thế sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:04.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I remember saying that we should always \Njust be good coworkers before.}Chị đã từng nói chúng ta\N là tiền bối và hậu bối tốt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But now...}Nhưng bây giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:13.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe now, it'd be okay if things changed.}Chị nghĩ thay đổi cũng không sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Like, for instance...}Nhưng là... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We... We...}Chúng ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We could be... friends.}Chúng ta có thể... là bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I mean, we already get along well, but—}À không, biết là đã thân nhau từ lâu nhưng--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:34.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Does that mean...}Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:40.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Does that mean you wouldn't mind if we spent \Nmore time together in our personal lives?}Chị không phiền nếu chúng ta liên quan \Nđến đời sống riêng tư của nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:44.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I can invite you out shopping?}Vậy em có thể mời chị đi mua sắm không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And for lunch on days off?}Và ăn trưa vào ngày nghỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If anything, I'd think that's \Na natural thing for friends to do!}Thì bạn bè làm vậy là bình thường mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:57.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A-And if I send you a text asking \N"Are you busy?" for no reason...}V-Và nếu chị có gửi tin nhắn vu vơ "Em rảnh không"...
