Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I wanted to go to that amusement park...}Mình muốn đi khu vui chơi ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai!}Chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:09.39,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{U-Um, I know the scheduling \Ndidn't work out for everyone, but...}E-Em biết lịch không trùng nhau nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Would you... well...}Liệu chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:21.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{as friends... we could...}như những người bạn, chúng ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:29.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What Yamagishi-san was talking about \Nsounded nice! So... maybe...}Em nghe Yamagishi nói tuyệt quá nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The amusement park.}Khu vui chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's go to the amusement park together.}Hãy đi khu vui chơi cùng nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:52.14,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{You said you were always free.}Cậu nói lúc nào cũng rảnh mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.57,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{But then you had a day \Nwhere you couldn't... Why?}Xong đến ngày mọi người rảnh thì \Nlại kêu bận, tị sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:58.15,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Well, let's just chalk it up \Nto doing the bro thing.}Đó là tình bạn giữa những người đàn ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The cute shoes I bought}Đôi giày mình vừa mua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{or the sneakers I've broken in...}Hay đôi sneaker mang nhiều lần...
