Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The fashionable look...}Một bộ đồ lịch sự...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.23,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Or the casual one...}Hay là đồ trẻ trung...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Which should I go with?}Chọn cái nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.50,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{You got a date?}Đi hẹn hò à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Don't just show up like that!}S-Sao chị lại vào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:44.42,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{You  always spend Golden Week every year \Nback at home, but this year you didn't.}Năm nào Tuần lễ vàng cũng ở nhà, \Nnhưng năm nay thì không nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.70,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{So I came to check on you.}Nên chị mày tò mò.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.21,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I see... a date with Shiorin, then.}Ra là hẹn hò với Shiorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:54.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{It's not a date! We're just going to \Nthe amusement park together!}Không phải hẹn hò! Bọn em đi khu vui chơi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:57.09,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Sounds like... a date.}Nghe khác gì hẹn hò không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, it's not!}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:01.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I haven't confessed to her \Nor started going out!}Em còn chưa tỏ tình nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:04.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We're really just going as friends!}Chỉ là bạn bè thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.49,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Then, you think...}Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:08.85,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{going to an amusement park \Nis something that friends do?}đi khu vui chơi là điều bạn bè hay làm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah.}P-Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.61,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H9D8D8B&\bord0\b1\fs18\shad0\frx6\fry28\frz350.5\move(320,362,320,188)}{Amusement Park Gate}
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.61,Italics,Announcement,0,0,0,,{Amusement Park Gate, Amusement Park Gate.}Cổng vào khu vui chơi! {Amusement Park Gate, Amusement Park Gate.}Cổng vào khu vui chơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.58,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I got here faster than I expected.}Mình đến hơi sớm nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.74,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should find a café...}Tìm quán cà phê nào ngồi chờ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.69,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess we were on the same train.}Có vẻ chúng ta đi cùng chuyến tàu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Cute!}Dễ thương!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I woke up a bit early.}Em dậy hơi sớm nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:40.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{M-Me, too.}C-Chị cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You seem different from usual.}Hôm nay chị trông khác ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.37,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Your hair's up, and you're wearing pants.}Tóc buộc lên và mặc quần dài.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:51.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Well, it's an amusement park...}Thì chúng ta đi khu vui chơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I figured we'd be walking a lot...}Chị nghĩ sẽ phải đi bộ nhiều...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I've got sneakers on, too.}Nên mang sneaker luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So do I.}Em cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We'll probably be walking more than \Nsome hiking trips, honestly.}Có lẽ chúng ta sẽ phải đi bộ nhiều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We're a little early, but let's get in line.}Có hơi sớm nhưng thôi xếp hàng đi chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:27.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's a senpai where I work...}Đàn chị chỗ làm của tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{who is tiny and cute.}vừa nhỏ xíu vừa dễ thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I guess we should head home.}Đến lúc về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess so.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But first...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{How about it? \NSomething to remember the occasion.}Thế nào? Chị muốn có một bức kỉ niệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-It's been a while since I've been \Nto an amusement park with a friend!}Đ-Đã lâu rồi chị chưa đi chơi cùng bạn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you not want to?}Em không muốn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I didn't say that!}Không phải là không...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.08,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Want me to take it for you?}Để tôi chụp cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you so—}Cảm ơn rất nhiều--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager?!}Quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:01.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Along with my sister and Hayakawa?! \NWhy are you here?!}Cả chị gái với Hayakawa nữa? Sao lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:05.38,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Li'l bro, you said as much yourself.}Em trai, em nói chứ còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.37,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Amusement parks are for visiting with your friends.}Khu vui chơi đi cùng bạn bè.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:09.80,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{And thus...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:13.21,Flashback,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Chihiro, let's go to the amusement park!}Chihiro, đi khu vui chơi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.12,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Let's invite Hayakawa-san, too, then.}Mời cả Hayakawa nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:17.31,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Huh? The amusement park?}Hả? Khu vui chơi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:21.56,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{And so, the three of us had a great time.}Và 3 bọn chị chơi cả ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:20.89,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Why am I here...?}Tại sao mình lại đi cùng...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:23.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I... see.}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:26.31,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Okay, now get closer together!}Rồi, ngồi sát vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:35.45,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Shiorin! Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:35.45,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san, did you enjoy yourself?}Hayakawa, em cũng vui mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.73,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well... I guess I did.}À thì vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:40.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Things got kind of busy \Nat the end there, but...}Đoạn cuối có hơi náo nhiệt nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.15,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Thinking of coming again?}Muốn đi nữa không?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.97,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I guess I am.}Vâng...
